data.description: Pre Foreclosure, amazing home on an amazing lot in a fantastic neighborhood. Price has been adjusted to reflect the updates needed. Four bedrooms, two and a half baths, spacious family room with a fireplace. Large backyard with an above ground pool that's in need of repair. This is a diamond in the rough, with your imagination and magic this is a true beauty. Perfect for entertaining, centrally located.   Please do not hesitate to call for specifics.
